This file marks the upstream agentic-dev-support-harness template repository.

Its presence means: this is the template source, not a project built from it.

harness-eject hard-refuses to run while this file exists, so the template
source can never be stripped of its setup machinery. The project-setup skill
removes this file as its final step when tailoring a downstream clone, which is
the only sanctioned way it leaves. Do not delete it from the source.

See docs/adr/adr-setup-introduce-harness-eject.md.
